\DOC handle

\TYPE {handle : (* signal -> (* -> void) -> void)}

\SYNOPSIS
Associates a signal handler with a particular signal.

\LIBRARY window

\DESCRIBE
{handle s h} associates the signal handler {h} with the signal {s}.
Now whenever {s} is raised {h} will be evaluated.

\FAILURE
Never fails.

\SEEALSO
clear, signal, sigtype.

\ENDDOC
